{{!--
  UiAction → native JS-free HTML via the {{action}} helper. The whole
  decision tree (anchor vs form-wrapped button, _method hidden field for
  DELETE/PUT, OPEN_IN_TAB target, confirm dialog) lives in
  SsrTriggerMapper.render() — keeping the template trivial avoids Handlebars
  conditionals on Trigger.method/behavior/payload at render time.

  Containers (form.hbs, detail.hbs, list-item.hbs) call this partial via
  {{> action this}}. Table row-actions need to substitute {id} per row, so
  table.hbs uses {{{rowAction this ../this}}} directly instead of this
  partial.
--}}
{{{action this}}}
